longBusinessSummary: Wolftank-Adisa Holding AG offers engineering and environmental protection services for contaminated soils and facilities, including remediation and monitoring of tank farms. It also designs, builds, refurbishes, extends and dismantles petrol stations. It also provides general contractor services to petrol stations. It provides double-walled renovation of flat bottom tanks and soil and groundwater purification. Wolftank-Adisa Holding AG is headquartered in Innsbruck, Austria and has additional locations in Italy, Austria, Germany, France, Russia, and China.
